item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Kylie Minogue - Better Than Today Promo (Lossless if poss)
item.description:
Just wondering if any kind soul here can help with a lossless version of this one

https://www.discogs.com/release/4038135-Kylie-Better-Than-Today

It's the version with the Club Junkies and Starlab mixes. Sadly it's one of the CDs I once had that was stolen that I'd never actually backed up! And as Discogs has it listed as an 'unofficial' release it means I cant just buy it (which it clearly wasn't as I was sent it by the PR at Parlophone in my DJ days)
